- Sostenlo, pues.

957
01:27:58,103 --> 01:27:59,820
¿Ves?

958
01:28:02,462 --> 01:28:05,135
No le harás daño.

959
01:28:12,181 --> 01:28:14,217
Gracias.

960
01:28:18,900 --> 01:28:21,049
